  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "This is a **scaffold template**, not a runnable application. It provides the infrastructure (commands, hooks, skills, agents, documentation templates) that makes Claude Code dramatically more effective. You use it to **create** projects, not run it directly.",
    "context": "[![CI](https://github.com/TheDecipherist/claude-code-mastery-project-starter-kit/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/TheDecipherist/claude-code-mastery-project-starter-kit/actions/workflows/ci.yml)\n\n> ## [View the Full Interactive Guide →](https://thedecipherist.github.io/claude-code-mastery-project-starter-kit/)\n>\n> The GitHub Pages site has the complete documentation with syntax highlighting, navigation, and visual examples.\n\n> The definitive starting point for Claude Code projects.\n> Based on [Claude Code Mastery Guides V1-V5](https://github.com/TheDecipherist/claude-code-mastery) by TheDecipherist.\n\n---",
